Package wtf.choco.veinminer.tool

Enum ToolCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ToolCategory>
      • wtf.choco.veinminer.tool.ToolCategory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ToolCategory>
    public enum ToolCategory
extends Enum<ToolCategory>
    Tool categories recognised by VeinMiner and it's code. Tool materials are limited to those listed in the enumeration.
